# ThisOne Project AI Guidelines

## Core AI Model
- Current Model: `gemini-2.5-flash`
- Definition Location: `js/config.js`
- **CRITICAL**: All AI-related calls must reference `AI_CONFIG.MODEL_NAME` (Node.js) or `window.ThisOneConfig.MODEL_NAME` (Browser).

## NEVER HARDCODE
- Do not manually write "gemini-x.x-flash" strings in any other files.
- If you need to change the model, update only `js/config.js`.

## Reason for strictness
- This version is validated for high-performance intelligent price comparison and market analysis within the Korean consumer electronics market.
